<h2>About NerdDinner</h2>
<h3>What is a "Dinner?"</h3>

<p>A "Dinner" in this application is simply an event, which can vary depending on what type of event the host wishes to have. A dinner consists of up to 8 components: <br /><br /></p>
<p><b>Title</b> - The name of the dinner &nbsp; <i style="color:red">[Required]</i></p>
<p><b>Event Date</b> - The date and time in which the dinner will take place &nbsp; <i style="color:red">[Required]</i></p>
<p><b>Description</b> - A description about what type of event the dinner will be &nbsp; <i style="color:red">[Required]</i></p>
<p><b>Address</b> - The address of where the dinner will take place (if at a physical location) &nbsp; <i style="color:dodgerblue">[Optional]</i></p>
<p><b>Country</b> - The country where the dinner will be hosted &nbsp;  <i style="color:dodgerblue">[Optional]</i></p>
<p><b>Contact Phone #</b> - A phone number in which guests can contact if they have any questions, concerns, or comments about the dinner &nbsp;  <i style="color:dodgerblue">[Optional]</i></p>
<p><b>Host</b> - The username of the host who created the dinner &nbsp;  <i style="color:blueviolet">[Automatically Generated]</i></p>
<p><b>Guests</b> - The usernames of the guests that RSVP'd to attend the dinner &nbsp;  <i style="color:darkgreen">[User-Generated]</i></p>
<br />
<h3>How do I RSVP to a Dinner?</h3>

<p>To RSVP to a dinner, you must first create and login to an account if you haven't already. To do this, you may use the "Register" button at the top right of the page.
    <br />Next, you will need to find a dinner you wish to RSVP to in the "Find Dinners" tab. Once you've found a dinner you wish to RSVP to, click on the title of the dinner and you
    will be brought to that dinner's details page where you will see a button you can click to RSVP. 
    If you wish to cancel your RSVP, you will simply need to click the "Cancel RSVP" button that appears on pages for dinners you are RSVP'd to.</p>